Our game, developed using Scratch, is an exciting five-stage adventure combining storytelling and problem-solving. The story follows a university student completing an assignment with the help of ChatGPT. Unexpectedly, the student clicks on a mysterious link and is pulled into a digital world controlled by ChatGPT itself.

In this new world, the student learns that the digital realm is in danger and must become a hero to save it. The player embarks on a thrilling journey through five unique stages:

1-Solving multiple puzzles.

2-Repairing a broken bridge.

3-Engaging in a shooting challenge.

4-Battling monsters.

5-Searching for tools to build an anti-volcano device.

After completing each stage, the player receives a special item that aids them in overcoming the next challenge.

Ultimately, the player restores balance to the digital world and safely returns to reality. This project highlights creativity, coding skills, and storytelling, emphasizing the power of AI and technology in interactive learning experiences.
